<body>
    <h1>=F0=9F=9A=80 BMAD Academy =E2=80=94 Your Guide to Building Smarter<=
/h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"f783292500c1" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=
=80=94YourGuidetoBuildingSmarter-=F0=9F=9A=80Module0=E2=80=94WelcometoBMADC=
hat!">=F0=9F=9A=80 Module 0 =E2=80=94 Welcome to BMAD Chat!</h1>
<p local-id=3D"44fc5171c8f1"><strong>Who this is for:</strong> Everyone =E2=
=80=94 yes, you too =F0=9F=91=8B <strong>Time to complete:</strong> ~20 min=
utes <strong>Vibe:</strong> Buckle up, it's going to be a good one.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b007cbb2-3820-47f1-8a6b-15a2ea169811">
<blockquote local-id=3D"afcf2e36-1fef-474b-99fe-869285309d9e">
<p local-id=3D"7c2d3b28cf80">=F0=9F=92=AC <em>"What if your team had a bril=
liant analyst, a sharp product manager, a seasoned architect, a coding wiza=
rd, and a QA ninja =E2=80=94 all available instantly, any time of day, and =
none of them in your Slack DMs asking for meeting links?"</em></p>
<p local-id=3D"1fa70d80321a">That's BMAD. Let's get into it.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr local-id=3D"14e84a99-179a-4bb8-a3a0-53360c29b825">
<h2 local-id=3D"aa5d2f2a6b69" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-=F0=9F=A4=94OkayBut...WhatEvenISBMAD?">=F0=9F=A4=94 =
Okay But... What Even IS BMAD?</h2>
<p local-id=3D"108c3d2c95ef"><strong>BMAD</strong> stands for <strong>Build=
 Me A Dream.</strong> And yes, it lives up to the name.</p>
<p local-id=3D"db4715098edd">At its heart, BMAD is a methodology =E2=80=94 =
a smart, structured way of using AI agents to take your team from a half-ba=
ked idea scribbled on a sticky note all the way to production-ready, tested=
, shipped software. Without losing your mind in the process.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7e003ccdeca4">Here's the fun part: it's not just one AI. It'=
s a <strong>whole crew</strong> of specialized agents, each with their own =
lane:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"a0=
1c7655-045c-45ea-ab5f-2b9e1cbe2ddb" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9d3fd4f7-86d2-41cc-b713-c7e970ea5bb5">
<th data-local-id=3D"7b64e46c-fd92-49bb-8455-c243e0f02f03" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9db8a146f30a">=F0=9F=A4=96 Agent</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"14dca7e3-7630-4724-a2f8-c41f59c21a7e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"30c41b0421dd">=F0=9F=8E=AF Their Superpower</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"1264b5e0-a37d-4d1c-bda0-a81a8f83bf13">
<td data-local-id=3D"d97fe52e-fd99-4376-ae22-83dd0a85b5b8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"933807778831">=F0=9F=94=8D <strong>Analyst (BA)</strong></p>=
</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3947f300-cc21-4564-86fa-bc0ca8f9e4a2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e0d630dd48db">Turns your vague ideas into crystal-clear requ=
irements</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9ed70289-8778-4751-b327-4e5980ce80e3">
<td data-local-id=3D"f3541671-f3f4-4e77-9bf2-216dda943125" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"04aac4dec81a">=F0=9F=93=8B <strong>Product Manager</strong><=
/p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8c2cac46-567a-48f0-ad16-954f4c00e2d1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ee29557c10ab">Chops requirements into epics, stories, and ta=
sks</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3c48c2e0-36e0-48da-b9f6-d85a849a15a1">
<td data-local-id=3D"52ed2ced-0362-45b3-8b5b-b9ffb83bc3cb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e3b2e6a3bf4d">=F0=9F=8F=97=EF=B8=8F <strong>Architect</stron=
g></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4f816f17-bac8-4e4c-b5c5-2158075058d7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"be437c4ab84f">Designs the technical blueprint so devs aren't=
 guessing</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"43f9e33b-fdf6-4198-ab87-9a43ddedb2aa">
<td data-local-id=3D"d189e52d-1ad1-49e6-a4f7-9f58d3aa61b3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4f532ebf016d">=F0=9F=92=BB <strong>Developer</strong></p></t=
d>
<td data-local-id=3D"236551ef-e698-4e9c-b8c5-4c6a2a8f3e04" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3d8d77b55163">Helps write, review, and refactor code like a =
senior dev on demand</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"bf4b20aa-2218-436c-94ac-782b59537e46">
<td data-local-id=3D"91d90b99-f48c-4c9a-b771-3ee55348c88d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"928e6fe95b98">=F0=9F=A7=AA <strong>QA Engineer</strong></p><=
/td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e35f88a3-836d-4877-b4ab-c384285d2871" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6e6209ae8adb">Generates test cases so nothing sneaks through=
 to prod</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"21016fcc-bf5c-46f3-908b-b63428dab689">
<td data-local-id=3D"a936d227-784e-40be-9f85-1a0bdd1fe56c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8f182cd4cbb4">=F0=9F=A7=AD <strong>Scrum Master</strong></p>=
</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7d67d139-c38f-4c21-a93b-d42770437a4b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"855f2a6dc75b">Keeps everyone moving and the chaos organized<=
/p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e4e90227-d60c-41be-83f0-74486a9079e2">
<td data-local-id=3D"a6cf94b8-ea80-4273-8889-db180289eb60" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0c89f5204943">=F0=9F=8E=A8 <strong>UX Designer</strong></p><=
/td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fef09ec8-4da0-436c-b83f-f0e1e37311cf" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bc5a80c0f4ba">Makes sure users actually enjoy what you build=
</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"110d045b43ef">None of these agents are here to take anyone's=
 job. They're here to do the <strong>heavy lifting on the boring stuff</str=
ong> so your team can focus on the decisions that actually need a human bra=
in. =F0=9F=A7=A0</p>
<hr local-id=3D"997c9c8d-e44f-4be4-963e-5bd120b08178">
<h2 local-id=3D"ad4a436a3504" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-=F0=9F=92=BBSoWhatisBMADChat?">=F0=9F=92=BB So What =
is BMAD Chat?</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e31cb9dc20d3">Think of BMAD Chat as the <strong>front door</=
strong> to the whole BMAD world. It's a web app where every role on your te=
am =E2=80=94 PO, Dev, QA, Scrum Master =E2=80=94 gets a guided, structured =
experience without needing to be an AI whisperer or a command-line ninja.</=
p>
<p local-id=3D"67efd644c8d6">Here's what's waiting for you inside:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"14bcf4325e04" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-=F0=9F=97=A8=EF=B8=8FClaudeDirectChat">=F0=9F=97=A8=
=EF=B8=8F Claude Direct Chat</h3>
<p local-id=3D"78e3bc5d4bb2">Your main interface for talking to the agents.=
 Pick an agent, describe what you're working on, and let it guide you. It's=
 conversational, intuitive, and surprisingly fun.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"8775fe57525f" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-=F0=9F=96=A5=EF=B8=8FPTYTerminal">=F0=9F=96=A5=EF=B8=
=8F PTY Terminal</h3>
<p local-id=3D"5123e21c186e">For the developers who want to get their hands=
 dirty. Full terminal access for deeper control. Power users, this one's fo=
r you.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"4fc33e0ae67e" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-=F0=9F=93=8AFeatureWorkflowDashboard">=F0=9F=93=8A F=
eature Workflow Dashboard</h3>
<p local-id=3D"5d40ba349ffe">A visual command center showing every feature =
your team is working on =E2=80=94 where it is in the lifecycle, what files =
exist, what's been created. No more "wait, where did we land on that featur=
e?" conversations.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"45e509274dfa" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-=F0=9F=97=82=EF=B8=8FMulti-ProductWorkspaces">=F0=9F=
=97=82=EF=B8=8F Multi-Product Workspaces</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c03378eea2d4">Working on more than one product? No problem. =
BMAD Chat supports multiple workspaces, each wired up to its own Git repo (=
GitHub or Azure DevOps). Everything stays organized and separate.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"f56df7ea3ff0" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-=F0=9F=94=90Oh,andSecurity?">=F0=9F=94=90 Oh, and Se=
curity?</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a4aa04aded86">You log in with your <strong>company Azure AD =
account</strong> =E2=80=94 same as your email and Microsoft 365. No new pas=
swords, no new accounts, no sticky notes on your monitor. Sessions are secu=
re, isolated, and sandboxed. Your IT team already loves this.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"9e84faa2-e574-4445-a640-f98d63dc855f">
<h2 local-id=3D"4f6a5fdaa2d9" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-=F0=9F=97=BA=EF=B8=8FTheBMADJourney=E2=80=94FromIdea=
toShipped">=F0=9F=97=BA=EF=B8=8F The BMAD Journey =E2=80=94 From Idea to Sh=
ipped</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c3a9a97c26dc">Here's the magic of BMAD in one beautiful flow=
. Every step has an agent. Every output lands somewhere useful.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">=F0=9F=
=92=A1 Someone has an idea
        =E2=86=93
=F0=9F=93=84 Analyst Agent =E2=86=92 Product Brief
        =E2=86=93
=F0=9F=93=8B PM Agent =E2=86=92 PRD (epics, stories, acceptance criteria)
        =E2=86=93
=F0=9F=8E=AB Automatic push =E2=86=92 JIRA tickets (your team picks them up=
!)
        =E2=86=93
=F0=9F=8F=97=EF=B8=8F Architect Agent =E2=86=92 Technical design
        =E2=86=93
=F0=9F=92=BB Dev picks up ticket =E2=86=92 Claude Code in VS Code helps bui=
ld it
        =E2=86=93
=F0=9F=A7=AA QA generates test cases =E2=86=92 bugs logged in JIRA
        =E2=86=93
=F0=9F=94=84 Bug webhook =E2=86=92 flows back into BMAD automatically
        =E2=86=93
=E2=9C=85 UAT sign-off by Product
        =E2=86=93
=F0=9F=9A=80 Rob hits the button =E2=86=92 Production!
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"20b2a6b572e5">From sticky-note idea to live feature. With ev=
ery role supported the whole way. Pretty neat, right?</p>
<hr local-id=3D"8acf1701-947c-4cf7-b294-d28caa78a021">
<h2 local-id=3D"bf534d206f3e" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-=F0=9F=8E=ABBMAD+JIRA=E2=80=94BetterTogether">=F0=9F=
=8E=AB BMAD + JIRA =E2=80=94 Better Together</h2>
<p local-id=3D"597fadb0bec4">JIRA and BMAD are best friends. Here's how the=
y talk to each other:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"44c2fbfb4f64" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-BMAD=E2=86=92JIRA(theeasypart)">BMAD =E2=86=92 JIRA =
<em>(the easy part)</em></h3>
<p local-id=3D"cfc2f611a5b7">When the PM agent finishes generating epics an=
d stories, they <strong>automatically push into JIRA</strong> as tickets. Y=
our team sees them on the board and starts picking them up. Zero copy-paste=
. Zero "can you format that as a story?" emails.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"a363930b6406" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-JIRA=E2=86=92BMAD(thecleverpart)">JIRA =E2=86=92 BMA=
D <em>(the clever part)</em></h3>
<p local-id=3D"be0ebf6475f5">QA engineers log bugs in JIRA the way they alw=
ays have. A <strong>webhook</strong> then automatically pulls those bugs ba=
ck into BMAD so developers can action them without leaving their workflow. =
Bugs in JIRA? Dev sees them in BMAD. Seamless.</p>
<blockquote local-id=3D"7e394576-07b1-426d-bbf1-fdb9f73297f9">
<p local-id=3D"5aa0dd75f32a">=E2=9A=A0=EF=B8=8F <strong>Heads up:</strong> =
Status updates are manual for now. This is intentional =E2=80=94 we're buil=
ding trust with AI-assisted workflows one step at a time. As confidence gro=
ws, so will the automation. Baby steps. =F0=9F=91=B6</p>
</blockquote>
<hr local-id=3D"72bd2ecb-0451-4da1-98f2-d01e58479a1a">
<h2 local-id=3D"8449f9bf63a0" id=3D"id-=F0=9F=9A=80BMADAcademy=E2=80=94Your=
GuidetoBuildingSmarter-=F0=9F=8C=8DYourThreeEnvironments=E2=80=94KnowThem,L=
oveThem">=F0=9F=8C=8D Your Three Environments =E2=80=94 Know Them, Love The=
m</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ef7af6d4ce88">Before you touch anything, get friendly with t=
hese three environments. They are sacred.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"7c=
e0ca84-8346-4abe-8f1a-e39aed5d654c" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6d348dba-efcb-4eb2-ad4c-ae7c320efa59">
<th data-local-id=3D"a99d7ff4-8b57-4ba4-988d-f7e2e1958370" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"65fabd01ebfd">=F0=9F=8F=A0 Environment</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"e9d916df-b85b-40d8-8e16-e359bda965e0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"04dcf65c9be3">=F0=9F=8E=AF Purpose</p></th>
